quran[3]{c,v,t,f}:
  2,19,"Tàbí (àpèjúwe wọn) dà bí òjò ńlá tí ń rọ̀ láti sánmọ̀. Ó mú àwọn òkùnkùn, àrá sísán àti mọ̀nàmọ́ná lọ́wọ́. Wọ́n ń fi ìka wọn sínú etí wọn nítorí àwọn iná láti ojú sánmọ̀ fún ìbẹ̀rù ikú. Allāhu sì yí àwọn aláìgbàgbọ́ ká."
  2,20,"Mọ̀nàmọ́ná náà fẹ́ẹ̀ mú ìríran wọn lọ. Ìgbàkígbà tí ó bá tan ìmọ́lẹ̀ sí wọn, wọ́n á rìn lọ nínú rẹ̀. Nígbà tí ó bá sì ṣóòòkùn mọ́ wọn, wọ́n á dúró si. Àti pé tí ó bá jẹ́ pé Allāhu bá fẹ́, dájúdájú ìbá gba ìgbọ́rọ̀ wọn àti ìríran wọn. Dájúdájú Allāhu ni Alágbára lórí gbogbo n̄ǹkan."
  2,21,"Ẹ̀yin ènìyàn, ẹ jọ́sìn fún Olúwa yín, Ẹni tí Ó dá ẹ̀yin àti àwọn tó ṣíwájú yín, nítorí kí ẹ lè máa bẹ̀rù Allāhu (kí ẹ sì lè ṣọ́ra fún ìyà Iná).{1}.",1:[Kalmọh “لَعَلَّ” “la‘alla” ní ìtúmọ̀ mẹ́ta. Ìrètí, nítorí àti ìgbájúmọ́ (dídúnnímọ́ n̄ǹkan).]
